---
description: Component patterns for Portfolio Kayro Gomes
globs: ["src/app/components/**/*"]
---
- Page components: `*Page.tsx` pattern (HomePage, ProjectsPage, AboutPage, ContactPage, CaseStudyPage)
- Layout: Header + Outlet + Footer in Layout.tsx
- DynamicName: Brand typography with dynamic letter-spacing
- ScrollZoomImage: Hero zoom-out effect (keep inline styles — dynamic)
- MermaidDiagram: Lazy-loaded, only flowchart + journey types
- ImageWithFallback: Protected component with SVG fallback
- Content files: `*Content.tsx` contain case study JSX, registered in `projects.ts`
- Do not reintroduce shadcn/ui components or `cn()` utility
- Form validation: Zod + react-hook-form in ContactPage
- FormSubmit POST with honeypot anti-spam field